  "texts": [
    "Regarding the use of an ombudsman the experts did not really see the purpose and necessity of an independent ombudsman in a requirements elicitation team, except of very difficult situations when the team itself cannot find a solution.",
    "Instead, they proposed to use coaching for supporting and guiding for openness appreciation, as well as shadowing experienced staff especially when an employee is involved in a multicultural team for the first time.",
    "This was viewed as an alternative approach for supporting problem solving, and for preventing possible problems.",
    "We consider that the role and meaning of the independent ombudsman is comparable to the role of the proposed coach.",
    "We changed the word \"ombudsman\" in the framework to the word \"coach\", which is a more understandable role, and more prevalent in the responses of the experts."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}